Judwaa - Episode 32 - 14th April 2025 [ Aina Asif & Adnan Raza Mir ] BERG OYSTER PEARL - HUM TV

Judwaa is the story of twin girls who share the same face but have contrasting personalities and destinies. One is gentle and reserved, while the other is bold and fearless. As fate weaves unexpected twists, their lives take dramatic turns. Starring Aina Asif in a dual role, this gripping drama explores identity, destiny, and the power of choice.

snippet.title: Rong Oi Rongali - Achurjya Borpatra | Sunit Gogoi | Pankaj Bora | New Bihu 2025
snippet.description:
Presenting official audio of #AchurjyaBorpatra's #RongOiRongali  (#AssameseSong) exclusively on Achurjya Borpatra Official.

"ৰঙ ঐ ৰঙালী" 
কণ্ঠ : আচুৰ্য বৰপাত্ৰ 
কথা - সুৰ - সংগীত পৰিচালনা : শোণিত গগৈ, পংকজ বৰা 
শব্দ সংমিশ্ৰণ : দিগন্ত বৰদলৈ 
সহযোগী কণ্ঠ : জনম কাশ্যপ, ৰাগদীপ চেতিয়া 
বাদ্য শিল্পী : 
ঢোল : পংকজ বৰা,লাচিত বৰুৱা,অংকুৰ বুঢ়াগোহাঁই 
তাল-পেঁপা-গগণা-ধূতং :
পিটি বৰা 
বাঁহী : কৈলাশ ৰাভা 
বাণীবন্ধন কক্ষ : ষ্টুডিঅ' অ'ডিঅহলিক 
বাণীবদ্ধক : স্বপ্নিল দত্ত, নিখিলেশ বৰা 
বিশেষ কৃতজ্ঞতা : বিশাল মহন বৰা, অভিনন্দন বৰা, প্ৰাণজিত নাথ 
হুঁচৰিটোৰ কিছু কথাংশ পৰম্পৰাগত ।

Label: AB Production
Music Publisher: Eikhon Axom Hoi Bhai Media

snippet.title: क्यों हमे जीते जी मार डालना चाहती हैं Prem Granth Movie Scene - Madhuri - Sulbha Arya - Om Puri
snippet.description:
Prem Granth is a 1996 Hindi romantic bollywood drama film starring Rishi Kapoor, Madhuri Dixit, Anupam Kher and Om Puri. The story revolves around Somen, son a Hindu priest of the village. Somen falls in love with Kajri who belongs to a lower caste and Somen’s family disapprove their relationship. When Kajri goes missing, Somen leaves his village to stay with his uncle. Will the lovers ever reunite?

💎 Movie : Prem Granth - प्रेम ग्रन्थ (1996)
💎 Director: Rajiv Kapoor - राजीव कपूर 
💎 Cast: 
    Shammi Kapoor - शम्मी कपूर as Nandlal
    Rishi Kapoor - ऋषि कपूर as Somen
    Madhuri Dixit - माधुरी दीक्षित as Kajri
    Anupam Kher - अनुपम खेर as Swami Dharam Bhooshan
    Om Puri - ओम पूरी as Baliram
    Prem Chopra - प्रेम चोपड़ा as Kedar Nath
    Reema Lagoo - रीमा लागू as Parvati
    Himani Shivpuri as Natho
    Sulabha Arya as Laxmi
    Govind Namdeo as Roop Sahai
💎 Music : Laxmikant–Pyarelal - लक्ष्मीकांत - प्यारेलाल 


#rishikapoor #madhuri #shammikapoor #anupamkher #romantic #latest #90s #90severgreen

Show Name: Gopal Bhar - গোপালভাঁড়
Directed By: Sourav Mondal, Hansa Mondal
Written By: Hansa Mondal
Original language: Bengali
Episode No: 1143

#GopalBhar #sonyaath #গোপালভর 

About Gopal Bhar:
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him as a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.

snippet.title: Adventure | Stand-up Comedy by Ravi Gupta
snippet.description:
When life gives you lemons, sell them and go to the mountains.
You’ll come back with beautiful memories and a sore body.

This is a story about a trek I did with my friend.
I spend a lot of time in the mountains. There’s no place more peaceful.
But the moment I have to walk on uneven ground, everything changes. My body starts questioning my soul.
It’s tough, annoying, and sometimes painful.
But once I’m back home, all that’s left is a funny story—and now, that story will stay with all of us forever.

Hope you enjoyed the video.
Please like, comment & share it.

I’m also performing my stand-up comedy special in the UK and touring across India and internationally!
Tickets for all my shows are live here: https://linktr.ee/Shudhdesicomic

Follow me on Instagram: 
@shudhdesicomic - https://www.instagram.com/shudhdesicomic

#raviguptacomedy #standupcomedy  #indianstandupcomedy  #comedy  #comedyvideo

snippet.title: राजस्थानी दाल ढोकली-जब कुकिंग का मन न हो तब बनायें-स्वादिष्ट व ईजी One-Pot Wholesome Meal Dal Dhokli
snippet.description:
पारंपरिक खाना-दाल में पकी नरम ढोकली-फटाफट वआसान- एक बर्तन में तैयार संपूर्ण भोजन,  Grandma’s Rajasthani Dal Dhokli Recipe – Pure Nostalgia, Spicy, Tangy, and Delicious – This Dal Dhokli Has It All

#daldhokli #onepotmeal #indianrecipe 

Ingredients for Rajasthani Dal Dhokla
अरहर दाल - Arhar dal - 1 cup (200 grams)
नमक - Salt - 1 tsp
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
टमाटर - Tomato - 2 no
गेहूं का आटा - Wheat flour - 1 cup
बेसन - Gram flour - 1/4 cup
नमक - Salt - 1/4 tsp
अजवाइन - Carom seeds - 1/4 tsp
लाल मिर्च पाउडर - Red chilli powder - 1/4 tsp
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
अदरक मिर्च पेस्ट - Ginger chilli paste - 1/2 tsp
हरा धनिया - Coriander - 1 tsp
घी - Ghee - 2 tbsp

For Tadka
घी - Ghee - 2-3 tbsp
जीरा - Cumin seeds - 1/2 tsp
हींग - Asafoetida - 1 pinch
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander powder - 1 tsp
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1 tsp, chopped
अदरक - Ginger - 1 tsp, grated
कश्मीरी लाल मिर्च - Kashmiri red chilli - 1 tsp
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli - 1/4 tsp, crushed
नमक - Salt - 1/2 tsp
अमचूर पाउडर - Dry mango powder - 1/2 tsp
गरम मसाला - Garam masala - 1/2 tsp
हरा धनिया - Coriander

snippet.title: ஒரு கப் ரசம் போதும், வேற எதுவும் வேணாம்! Tomato Rasam This Tasty? Chef Deena's Kitchen
snippet.description:
Kalyana Veetu Rasam
Ready to unlock the secret to that irresistible wedding rasam? Chef Deena is on a mission, and he's teamed up with Chennai's very own young culinary whiz, Mr. Harish from Janani Catering Services in West Mambalam!  Get ready to learn the nuances of an aromatic and flavorful rasam recipe, a staple at South Indian weddings, as Mr. Harsh guides us through the step-by-step process. Let's dive in and discover the magic of Janani Catering's Kalyanam Rasam! 

Sri Janani Catering Service
Mr. Harish
Contact : 9840703703

கல்யாண வீட்டு ரசம் | Kalyaana Veettu Rasam (Wedding-Style Rasam)
Thakkali Rasam
Tomato - 1 Kg
Mustard - 1 Tsp
Cumin Seeds - 1 Tsp
Pepper - 35 g
Asafoetida - 1 Tsp
Tamarind - 100 g
Jaggerry - 1/2 Tsp
Chrushed Garlic - 100 g
Dry Red Chilli - 6 to 7 Nos 
Green Chilli - 6 to 7 Nos
Curry Leaves - As Required 
Coriander Leaves - As Required 
Turmeric Powder - 1/2 Tsp
Salt - To Taste 
Gingelly Oil - 200 ml 
Ghee - For Tempering
 


My Amazon Store { My Picks and Recommended Product }
https://www.amazon.in/shop/chefdeenaskitchen

_______________
Hello!!  My Name is chef Deena from the popular Adupangarai show in Jaya TV Viewers must have seen me in Zee Tamil shows as well.  My Culinary journey as a trainee to become an Executive Chef is incredible. My experience in the culinary field is for more than fifteen years and my USP is Indian cooking !! Apart from being a TV cookery host, my experience lies mainly with being employed in some of the major star hotels across the country especially the Marriott group.

     Chef Deena Cooks is my English Youtube Channel! Practical, simple recipes are my forte and using minimal easily available ingredients is my hallmark. Rudiments of cooking and baking are taught from scratch and any amateur cook can learn to make exciting dishes by watching my channel!  Also, Cooking traditional foods, Easy cooking Recipes, Healthy Snacks, Indian curries, gravies, Baking and Millions of other homemade treats. 

Subscribe to Chef Deena Cooks (CDK) for more cooking videos.

snippet.title: என்னுடைய தம்பிக்கு நிச்சயதார்த்தம் / புது பொன்னுமாப்பிளையை பார்க்கலாம் வாங்க / Engagement function,
snippet.description:
#Engagementfunction

என்னுடைய தம்பிக்கு நிச்சயதார்த்தம் / புது பொன்னுமாப்பிளையை பார்க்கலாம் வாங்க / Engagement function 

#wetting 
#weddingphotography 
#villageEngagement
#simplevillageEngagemen
#Engagement 

#engagementvideo 

#engagementvideotamil
#engagementvideodance

வணக்கம் நண்பர்களே 🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏  
தங்கள் இல்லங்களில் நடைபெறும் அனைத்து விசேஷங்களுக்கும், பிறந்த நாள்,திருமண நாள் திருமண நாள்  நினைவு நாள் மற்றும் இதர விசேஷங்களுக்கும் நீங்கள் எங்கள் மூலமாக சிரமப்படும் மக்களுக்கு உணவு ,உணவு பொருள்கள் ,மற்றும் வீடு இல்லாதவர்களுக்கு வீடு கட்டி கொடுக்க மற்றும் கணவரை இழந்து வருமானம் இன்றி  வாடும் பெண்களுக்கு அவர்களின் வாழ்வாதாரத்திற்கு அவர்களுக்கு ,ஆடு,மாடு, பெட்டிக்கடை,தையல் இயந்திரம் ,மாவு அரைக்கும் இயந்திரம் மற்றும் ஊனமுற்றவர்களுக்கு உதவிகள் ,குழந்தைகளின் படிப்பு செலவுகளுக்கு மற்றும் இன்னும் நிறைய உதவிகள் எங்கள்   My Country Foods சேனல் மூலமாக நீங்கள் செய்ய விரும்பினால்  இந்த மெயில் IDக்கு மெயில் அனுப்பவும்   anandhaeswari4@gmail.com நாங்கள் உங்களை விரைவில் தொடர்பு கொள்வோம்

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 4371 | 14 Apr 2025 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4371: Bapuji’s Race Against Time
--------------------------------------------------------
With time running out, Bapuji hopes to catch up with Mannu before his flight to America. An unexpected detour slows him down as he looks for a way to reach in time.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4371 | 14 Apr 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1090476720

Lakh sitaron ki ek thi dua
Dil pe tabhi to zor na chala

Khudaya ishq re ishq re ishq re

Khudaya ishq hote hote ho gaya

Jaise dariya ka behta paani

Kehti hai nazar deewani

Ik tu naya naya sa
Aur dunia lage puraani

Saari taarikhon pe haq hai tera
Aur kya chahun tu hai mera

snippet.title: Gokuldham के Gents को क्यों पहननी पड़ी साड़ी?| Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | 14 Apr 2025
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Jetha finds himself in a tricky situation one side is his wife and another side his best friend on whose victory he should be happy. Daya wins the arm wrestling and Jetha claps and appreciates her. Jetha and Sundar come face to face for arm wrestling and Jetha wins. All first-round winners go into the second round. Jetha and Champak face each other in arm wrestling and Champak wins. About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: श्री हनुमान जन्मोत्सव | Shree Hanuman Janmotsav | Dr Kumar Vishwas
snippet.description:
मनोजवं मारुततुल्यवेगं, जितेन्द्रियं बुद्धिमतां वरिष्ठम्। वातात्मजं वानरयूथमुख्यं, श्रीरामदूतं शरणं प्रपद्ये॥
आप सबको शक्ति और शालीनता के एकल पर्याय, विद्या के सर्वश्रेष्ठ प्रतीक, बजरंग बली महावीर हनुमान जन्मोत्सव की पूर्व संध्या पर ढेर सारी शुभकामनाएँ! 🙏🏻💐इस पुण्य-अवसर पर अपने-अपने राम ऊर्जा-सत्र का यह विशेष प्रसंग आप सबकी आस्था को सादर समर्पित है। 😍🙏🏻
#kumarvishwas #hanumanjanmotsav #apneapneram 

Follow us on :- 

YouTube :- http://youtube.com/KumarVishwas
Facebook :- https://www.facebook.com/KumarVishwas
Twitter :- https://twitter.com/DrKumarVishwas
Instagram :- https://www.instagram.com/KumarVishwas

Subscribe To Our Other YouTube Channels:-

Apne Apne Ram    : https://www.youtube.com/@ApneApneRamOfficial
  
The KV Studio        : https://www.youtube.com/@TheKVStudio

Apne Apne Shyam : https://www.youtube.com/@ApneApneShyamOfficial

-------------------------------------------------------------------
About Dr Kumar Vishwas :

The people who make history are the ones who not only give their life to their career but also give their career a new life. When the career is that of a poet, every step is a risk. Kumar Vishwas is one such poet who has gifted himself an era of such a popularity which other poets cant’t even dream of.
Kumar Vishwas is a poet who went beyond the stereotypical norms of ‘Kavi Sammelan’ or poetic functions and made it a performer’s stage. He has mastered and excelled in all aspects in whatever he has done. Dr Kumar Vishwas has been doing this since years just with a mic and his poems and wits in his soulful voice.
His popularity can be guessed by the fact that the audience sings his verses with him, he has crafted a new dimension by rejuvenating the structure and mechanics of Hindi poetry and Kavi Sammelan.
 
Recently, Dr. Kumar Vishwas has started hosting energy sessions popularly Known as Apne Apne Ram and Apne Apne Shyam where he talks about life skills of Shri Ram’s and Shri Krishna's life, and the applicability of the same in one’s own life to over come the challenges and social concerns we come across in our life.

snippet.description:
#tamilnewyear2025 #தமிழ்ப்புத்தாண்டு #தமிழ்வருடப்பிறப்பு
#தமிழ்ப்புத்தாண்டு #தமிழ்வருடப்பிறப்பு 

சித்திரை மாதத்தில் பிறந்தவர்களும், குழந்தை பெற்றவர்களும் பார்க்க வேண்டிய பதிவு | Desa Mangayarkarasi
https://youtu.be/XxAB_XVBMZo

மருத்து நீராடி தமிழ்ப் புத்தாண்டை வரவேற்று வழிபடும் முறை | கனி காணுதல் | தமிழ் வருட பிறப்பு
https://youtu.be/0g00MJwEQNw

செல்வம், ஆரோக்கியம், நீண்ட ஆயுள் பெற தமிழ்ப் புத்தாண்டை வரவேற்று வழிபடும் முறை.   மேலும் கனி காணுதல், அறுசுவை உணவு படைத்தல், வழிபடும் நேரம் என பல தகவல்களை திருமதி. தேச மங்கையர்க்கரசி அம்மா அவர்கள் அளித்துள்ளார். 

- ஆத்ம ஞான மையம்

snippet.description:
Gokuldham Society | Gada Electronics | Bonus | Financial Year

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. Are you ready for the challenge? 

 Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  #GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame


Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

en-US.description:

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. Are you ready for the challenge? 

 Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  #GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Mann Mast Malang Episode 25 Teaser - 13th April 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Mann Mast Malang is a love story that traces the journey of two families who, once close and united by their children's engagement, become sworn enemies due to a single incident. As the story unfolds, Kabeer and Riya, former fiancés turned enemies, start to grow closer and eventually fall in love. Their love story faces the challenge of uniting their feuding families, as they strive to make their love successful against all odds.

aankh meri ye aari tu padjaga katke,,,
jhaaj ke main beth gori Raam Ratke,,

Teri khanke payal kargi ghayal beth kun main chand rove ,,,
meri aankh main kajal barse badal bin mosam barsat hove,,,
yogi Amarjeet kyu teri aankhya main khatke,,,

Sinulla on 10 päivää aikaa ansaita mahdollisimman monta palkintoa, joihin lukeutuu myös ULTRAPOKAALILIPAS! 😱

🎯 Laskemme tyrmäyksiä. Pistä siis töpinäksi ja ala tyrmätä muita rämäpäitä!
🔓 Jokaisen etapin avaamiseen vaaditaan miljardi tyrmäystä. Voit lunastaa palkintosi etapin suorittamista seuraavan kaupan päivittäisen päivityksen yhteydessä!
🙌  Palkintoja on tarjolla rajaton määrä. Kyse on siis nopeudesta!

✨ERITYINEN ARVONTA✨

🎫 Voit voittaa Brawl Pass Plussan KOKO VUODEKSI (yht. 12 passia) ja 10 Brawl Pass Plussaa jaettavaksi kavereidesi kanssa! 🤯
👀 MITEN? Julkaise siistein peliliikkeesi somessa tunnisteella #BrawlStarsP2W. Valitsemme 5 onnekasta voittajaa tapahtuman päätyttyä!

nl.title: ONS ALLEREERSTE P2W-COMMUNITYEVENEMENT?!
nl.description:
Het is het... 'PLAY TO WIN'-COMMUNITYEVENEMENT! 🥵🔥

Je hebt 10 dagen de tijd om zo veel mogelijk beloningen te krijgen, waaronder een ULTRA-TROFEEËNDOOS! 😱

🎯 We tellen UITSCHAKELINGEN, dus het enige wat je hoeft te doen is andere knokkers ^£#*@$!
🔓 Elke mijlpaal vereist 1 miljard uitschakelingen en na het voltooien van een mijlpaal, kun je de beloningen claimen bij de volgende dagelijkse winkel-reset!
🙌 Er is geen beloningenlimiet voor dit evenement. De enige limiet is tijd!

✨SPECIALE WEGGEEFACTIE✨

🎫 Je kunt een HEEL jaar aan Brawl Pass Plus winnen (12 in totaal) + 10 Brawl Passes Plus om te delen met je vrienden! 🤯
👀 HOE? Post je beste gameplay op sociale media met de hashtag #BrawlStarsP2W en wij kiezen de 5 gelukkige winnaars nadat het evenement afloopt!

zh-Hans.title: 首次“P2W”社区活动？
zh-Hans.description:
这里的“P”，不是付费（Pay），而是代表玩（Play）！隆重介绍“玩就能赢”社区活动！🥵🔥

在10天内，大家可以尽情赢取奖励，其中包括一个究极荣誉宝箱！😱

🎯 本次活动我们将记录击倒数！所以大家要做的，就是把对手的英雄都^£#$掉！
🔓 每累积10亿次击倒，即可达成一个里程碑。完成一个里程碑之后，对应的奖励会在第二天商店刷新时出现，记得领取哦！
🙌 本次活动可获取的奖励不设上限，唯一的限制就是活动的持续时间！

✨ 特别赠礼活动！✨

🎫 你有机会通过赠礼活动赢得一整年的高级乱斗金券（总共12个），另外还有10个高级乱斗金券可以赠送给好友！🤯
👀 如何参加？在社交媒体上分享你的游戏高光时刻，并且在贴文中加上话题标签#BrawlStarsP2W，我们会在活动结束后选出5位幸运玩家，送上惊喜赠礼！

zh-Hant.title: 首次「P2W」社群活動？
zh-Hant.description:
這裡的「P」，不是付費（Pay），而是代表玩（Play）！隆重介紹「玩就能贏」社群活動！🥵🔥

在10天內，大家可以盡情贏取獎勵，其中包括一個究極榮耀寶箱！😱

🎯 本次活動我們將記錄擊殺數！所以大家要做的，就是把對手的英雄都^£#$掉！
🔓 每累積10億次擊殺，即可達成一個里程碑。完成一個里程碑之後，對應的獎勵會在第二天商店刷新時出現，記得領取唷！
🙌  本次活動可獲取的獎勵不設上限，唯一的限制就是活動的持續時間！

✨ 特別抽獎活動！✨

🎫 你有機會透過抽獎活動贏得一整年的高級亂鬥通行券（總共12個），另外還有10個高級亂鬥通行券可以贈送好友！🤯
👀 如何參加？在社群媒體上分享你的遊戲精彩時刻，並且在貼文中加上hashtag #BrawlStarsP2W，我們會在活動結束後選出5位幸運玩家，送上這份驚喜！

pt-BR.title: NOSSO PRIMEIRO EVENTO PeG?
pt-BR.description:
Chegou o evento da comunidade PARTICIPE E GANHE! 🥵🔥

Você tem 10 dias para conseguir o máximo de recompensas possível, incluindo uma ULTRACAIXA DE TROFÉUS! 😱

🎯 Estamos contando as ELIMINAÇÕES, então você só precisa ^£#$@% os outros Brawlers!
🔓 Cada marco requer 1 bilhão de eliminações e, assim que a meta é atingida, você pode reivindicar as recompensas na próxima atualização da loja!
🙌 Não há limite de recompensas no evento, o único é o tempo!

✨SORTEIO ESPECIAL✨

🎫 Você pode ganhar um ano INTEIRO de Brawl Pass Plus (12 no total) + 10 Brawl Passes Plus para dar aos amigos! 🤯
👀 COMO? Publique sua melhor jogada nas redes sociais usando a hashtag #BrawlStarsP2W, e nós escolheremos 5 sortudos quando o evento acabar!

ru.title: ПЕРВОЕ В ИСТОРИИ СОБЫТИЕ СООБЩЕСТВА P2W?!
ru.description:
Встречайте... СОБЫТИЕ СООБЩЕСТВА PLAY TO WIN — «ИГРАЙ, ЧТОБЫ ПОБЕДИТЬ!» 🥵🔥

У вас будет 10 дней на получение наград, в числе которых — трофейный ультраящик! 😱

🎯 В этом событии мы считаем победы над бойцами, так что ваша задача — ^£#$ других бойцов!
🔓 Для каждого рубежа нужно набрать 1 миллиард побед, а после его достижения вы сможете забрать награды со следующим обновлением магазина.
🙌 В этом событии нет ограничений на награды — только на время!

✨ОСОБАЯ РАЗДАЧА ПОДАРКОВ✨

🎫 Вы можете выиграть годовой запас Brawl Pass Plus (всего 12 пропусков), а также 10 Brawl Pass Plus в подарок для своих друзей! 🤯
👀 КАК? Поделитесь записью своего лучшего игрового момента в соцсети, добавив хэштег #BrawlStarsP2W, и мы выберем 5 победителей в конце события!

en.title: OUR FIRST EVER P2W COMMUNITY EVENT?!
en.description:
It's the... PLAY TO WIN COMMUNITY EVENT! 🥵🔥

You have 10 days to get as many rewards as possible, including an ULTRA TROPHY BOX! 😱

🎯 We're tracking TAKEDOWNS! So all you have to do is ^£#$ other Brawlers!
🔓 Each milestone requires 1 billion takedowns and after completing a milestone, you can claim the rewards on the next Shop daily refresh!
🙌 There is no reward limit for this event, the only limit is time!

✨SPECIAL GIVEAWAY✨

🎫 You can win a WHOLE year of Brawl Pass Plus (12 in total!) + 10 Brawl Passes Plus to share with your friends! 🤯
👀 HOW? Post your best play on social media using the hashtag #BrawlStarsP2W, and we’ll choose the 5 lucky winners after the event ends!

Download NOW!! ►► https://supr.cl/2K62CZG
Subscribe!! ►► https://supr.cl/subscribe

id.title: ACARA KOMUNITAS P2W PERTAMA?!
id.description:
Ini dia ... ACARA KOMUNITAS PLAY TO WIN! 🥵🔥

Kamu punya 10 hari untuk mendapatkan sebanyak mungkin hadiah yang mencakup KOTAK TROFI ULTRA! 😱

🎯 Jumlah TUMBANG akan dicatat! Kamu cuma perlu &=^£#~$ Jagoan lain!
🔓 Setiap ambang perlu 1 miliar tumbang dan setelah suatu ambang tercapai, kamu bisa mengambil hadiah pada penyegaran harian Toko yang berikutnya!
🙌 Hadiah di acara ini tidak terbatas, yang terbatas cuma waktunya!

✨BAGI-BAGI HADIAH SPESIAL✨

🎫 Kamu bisa mendapatkan Brawl Pass Plus untuk SEPANJANG tahun (totalnya 12!) + 10 Brawl Pass Plus untuk dibagikan kepada teman! 🤯
👀 CARANYA? Unggah permainan terbaikmu di media sosial dengan tagar #BrawlStarsP2W dan kami akan memilih 5 pemenang beruntung setelah acara berakhir!

tr.title: İLK P2W TOPLULUK ETKİNLİĞİMİZ!
tr.description:
KAZANMAK İÇİN OYNA TOPLULUK ETKİNLİĞİ başlıyor! 🥵🔥

Bir ULTRA KUPA KUTUSU da dahil, olabildiğince fazla ödül almak için 10 gününüz var! 😱

🎯 YOK ETTİĞİNİZ RAKİPLERİ sayıyoruz! Tek yapmanız gereken diğer savaşçıların hakkından gelmek!
🔓 Her eşik için 1 milyar rakip yok etmeniz gerekiyor ve eşiklere ulaştıktan sonra kazandığınız ödülleri dükkandaki ödüller yenilendiğinde alabileceksiniz!
🙌 Bu etkinlikte ödül sınırı yok, tek sınır süre!

✨ÖZEL ÇEKİLİŞ✨

🎫 Kendiniz için BÜTÜN bir yıllık (toplam 12 adet!) Brawl Pass Plus ve arkadaşlarınızla paylaşabileceğiniz 10 Brawl Pass Plus kazanabilirsiniz! 🤯
👀 NASIL MI? Oyundaki en iyi anlarınızı #BrawlStarsP2W etiketini kullanarak sosyal medya hesabınızda paylaşın. Etkinlik sona erdiğinde beş şanslı kazananı seçeceğiz!

es.title: ¿EL PRIMER EVENTO DE LA COMUNIDAD P2W?
es.description:
¡Llega el evento de la comunidad Play to Win (juega para ganar)! 🥵🔥

Consigue todas las recompensas que puedas en 10 días, entre ellas, ¡una caja de trofeos ultra! 😱

🎯 Llevaremos la cuenta de las eliminaciones. ¡Así que ya sabes, solo tienes que ^£&#$ a otros brawlers!
🔓 Cada meta requiere mil millones de eliminaciones, y tras alcanzar cada meta, las recompensas aparecerán en la tienda al día siguiente para que las reclames.
🙌 Este evento no tiene límite de recompensas, ¡solo de tiempo!

✨SORTEO ESPECIAL✨

🎫 Puedes ganar un año entero del Brawl Pass Plus, es decir, 12 pases en total, y 10 pases adicionales para que los compartas con tus amigos. 🤯
👀 ¿Cómo? Comparte tu mejor partida en tus redes sociales con el hashtag #BrawlStarsP2W y elegiremos a 5 ganadores después de que termine el evento.

it.title: IL PRIMO EVENTO PxV DELLA COMMUNITY!
it.description:
Scopri l'evento della community PARTECIPA PER VINCERE! 🥵🔥

Hai 10 giorni per accumulare quante più ricompense possibili, tra cui una CASSA ULTRA DEI TROFEI! 😱

🎯 Terremo il conto delle ELIMINAZIONI, perciò ti dovrai solo concentrare e fare il ^£#$ a un bel po' di brawler nemici!
🔓 Per raggiungere ogni traguardo, servirà un miliardo di eliminazioni e, una volta sbloccata la ricompensa corrispondente, la potrai ritirare dal negozio non appena si aggiornano le sue offerte.
🙌 In questo evento, le ricompense accumulabili sono infinite! L'unico limite è il tempo.

✨IL CONCORSO SPECIALE✨

🎫 Potrai vincere un anno INTERO di Brawl Pass Plus (ben 12 in totale) e altri 10 Brawl Pass Plus da condividere con gli amici! 🤯
👀 VUOI PARTECIPARE ANCHE TU? Pubblica la tua giocata migliore sui social includendo nel post l'hashtag #BrawlStarsP2W e, alla fine dell'evento, sceglieremo i cinque vincitori!

pl.title: NASZE PIERWSZE WYDARZENIE SPOŁECZNOŚCIOWE P2W?!
pl.description:
Przedstawiamy... WYDARZENIE SPOŁECZNOŚCIOWE GRAJ I WYGRYWAJ! 🥵🔥

Macie 10 dni, aby zdobyć jak najwięcej nagród, w tym ULTRASKRZYNKĘ PUCHARÓW! 😱

🎯 Liczą się ELIMINACJE! Waszym zadaniem jest więc ^£#$ innych Zadymiarzy!
🔓 Każdy kamień milowy wymaga 1 miliarda eliminacji, a gdy zostanie osiągnięty, nagrody można odebrać w sklepie po kolejnym codziennym odświeżeniu.
🙌 W tym wydarzeniu nie obowiązuje żaden limit nagród. Jedynym limitem jest czas!

✨ROZDANIE SPECJALNE✨

🎫 Możecie wygrać Karnety Zadymiarskie plus NA CAŁY rok (w sumie 12!) + 10 Karnetów Zadymiarskich plus do podziału ze znajomymi! 🤯
👀 JAK? Udostępnijcie swoje najlepsze rozgrywki na mediach społecznościowych, używając hasztagu #BrawlStarsP2W, a my po zakończeniu wydarzenia wybierzemy 5 szczęśliwych zwycięzców.

de.title: UNSER ALLERERSTES P2W-COMMUNITY-EREIGNIS?!
de.description:
Es ist das ... PLAY-TO-WIN-COMMUNITY-EREIGNIS! 🥵🔥

Du hast zehn Tage Zeit, um so viele Belohnungen wie möglich zu erhalten, unter anderem eine ULTRA-TROPHÄENBOX! 😱

🎯 Wir erfassen TAKEDOWNS! Du musst also nur andere Brawler ^£#$!
🔓 Jeder Meilenstein erfordert eine Milliarde Takedowns und nach Erreichen eines Meilensteins kannst du die Belohnungen nach der nächsten täglichen Aktualisierung des Shops abholen!
🙌 Für dieses Ereignis gibt es kein Limit an Belohnungen – das einzige Limit ist die Zeit!

✨BESONDERES GIVEAWAY✨

🎫 Du kannst den Brawlpass Plus für ein GANZES Jahr gewinnen (insgesamt zwölf Pässe!) und außerdem zehn Brawlpässe Plus zum Teilen mit deinen Freunden! 🤯
👀 WIE? Poste deinen besten Spielzug mit dem Hashtag #BrawlStarsP2W auf Social Media. Wir wählen die fünf glücklichen Gewinner nach dem Ende des Ereignisses aus!

ar.title: هل هذا حدث P2W الأول على الإطلاق لمجتمع اللعبة؟
ar.description:
إنه حدث مجتمع اللعبة ’العب للفوز‘ 🥵🔥

أمامكم 10 أيام للحصول على أكبر عدد ممكن من المكافآت، بما في ذلك صندوق 😱

🎯 نحن نتابع عدد الإطاحات، لذلك كل ما عليكم فعله هو الإطاحة بالأبطال الآخرين.
🔓 يتطلب كل إنجاز القيام بمليار إطاحة، وبعد إكمال الإنجاز يمكنكم المطالبة بالمكافآت في التحديث اليومي التالي للمتجر.
🙌 لا يوجد حد مكافآت لهذا الحدث، الحد الوحيد هو الوقت.

✨هدية خاصة✨

🎫  يمكنكم ربح سنة كاملة من Brawl Pass Plus (12 شهرًا كاملاً) + 10 تذاكر Brawl Pass Plus لمشاركتها مع أصدقائكم. 🤯
👀 كيف ذلك؟ بإرسال أفضل لحظات لعبكم على وسائل التواصل الاجتماعي باستخدام وسم #BrawlStarsP2W وسنختار الفائزين الخمسة المحظوظين بعد انتهاء الحدث.

ko.title: 브롤스타즈 사상 최초의 과금 커뮤니티 이벤트?!
ko.description:
사실은... '과하게 금 같은' 커뮤니티 이벤트랍니다! 🥵🔥

10일 동안 울트라 트로피 상자를 비롯해 최대한 많은 보상을 챙기세요! 😱

🎯 이번 이벤트에서는 테이크다운을 집계합니다! 그러니 다른 브롤러를 처치하기만 하면 되는 거죠!
🔓 마일스톤당 10억 테이크다운이 필요하며, 마일스톤 하나를 완료하면 다음 상점 새로고침 후에 보상을 수령할 수 있습니다!
🙌 이번 이벤트는 보상 한도가 없으며, 시간 제한만 있습니다!

✨특별 선물✨

🎫 1년 내내 브롤 패스 플러스(총 12개)를 받을 기회를 잡으세요! 게다가 덤으로, 친구에게 나눠줄 수 있는 10개의 브롤 패스 플러스도 드립니다! 🤯
👀 참여 방법: 소셜 미디어에서 게시물에 #BrawlStarsP2W 해시태그를 사용해 최고의 플레이 장면을 공유하세요. 이벤트 종료 후 행운의 당첨자 5명을 선정할 예정입니다!

fr.title: NOTRE TOUT PREMIER ÉVÉNEMENT COMMUNAUTAIRE P2W ?!
fr.description:
Voici... L'ÉVÉNEMENT COMMUNAUTAIRE PLAY TO WIN ! 🥵🔥

Vous avez 10 jours pour gagner autant de récompenses que possible, y compris une ULTRA BOÎTE DES TROPHÉES ! 😱

🎯 C'est les éliminations qui comptent, donc tout ce que vous avez à faire, c'est de ^£#$ des brawlers !
🔓 Vous atteignez chaque palier au bout d'un milliard d'éliminations. Vous pourrez récupérer les récompenses des paliers atteints à la prochaine réinitialisation quotidienne du magasin !
🙌 Il n'y a pas de limite de récompenses pour cet événement, seul le temps est limité !

✨CONCOURS SPÉCIAL✨

🎫 Vous pouvez gagner une année entière de Pass Brawl Plus (12 au total !) + 10 Pass Brawl Plus à partager avec vos amis ! 🤯
👀 COMMENT FAIRE ? Partagez vos plus belles actions sur les réseaux avec le hashtag #BrawlStarsP2W et nous choisirons les 5 gagnants après la fin de l'événement !

ja.title: ブロスタ初となるP2Wコミュニティイベント！
ja.description:
「P2W」とは「プレイ・トゥ・ウィン」の略です 🥵🔥

10日間のイベント期間中、ウルトラトロフィーボックス1個を含む報酬が無限に獲得可能です 😱

🎯 今回の目標は「撃破数」！できるだけ多くの対戦相手をブッ※※しましょう！
🔓 各目標の達成には「10億撃破」が必要です。目標を達成すると、毎日のショップ更新の際に報酬が回収可能になります！
🙌 本イベントでは報酬の獲得数に上限がありません。時間の続く限り報酬を回収しましょう！

✨特別プレゼント企画✨

🎫 ブロスタパス＋の年間パス（12カ月分）＆追加のブロスタパス＋10個（フレンドへの寄付用）をプレゼント 🤯
👀 最高のプレイ動画にハッシュタグ「#BrawlStarsP2W」を添えて、SNSに投稿しましょう。5名の幸運な当選者をイベント終了後に発表します！

Mann Mast Malang Digitally Presented by Diamond Paints & Nestle Lactogrow

Mann Mast Malang is a love story that traces the journey of two families who, once close and united by their children's engagement, become sworn enemies due to a single incident. As the story unfolds, Kabeer and Riya, former fiancés turned enemies, start to grow closer and eventually fall in love. Their love story faces the challenge of uniting their feuding families, as they strive to make their love successful against all odds.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 4370 | 12 Apr 2025 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4370: Bapuji’s Race Against Time
--------------------------------------------------------
With time running out, Bapuji hopes to catch up with Mannu before his flight to America. An unexpected detour slows him down as he looks for a way to reach in time.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4370 | 12 Apr 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS! De Bruyne inspires stunning five-star City fightback! | Man City 5-2 Crystal Palace
snippet.description:
A Kevin De Bruyne-inspired City staged a stunning comeback from 2-0 down to overwhelm Crystal Palace 5-2 at the Etihad and so step up our charge for a Champions League place.

In what was a remarkable, incident-packed game, the Eagles had soared into an early two-goal lead through Eberechi Eze and Chris Richards and saw a potential third by Eze ruled out by VAR for offside.

But, in his first appearance at the Etihad since confirmation that he is to leave City this summer after 10 glorious years, skipper De Bruyne helped spark a quite magnificent comeback.

The Belgian first narrowed the deficit with a trademark first half free-kick before then being involved in Omar Marmoush’s leveller before the break.

De Bruyne it was who then set up Mateo Kovacic a minute after the restart to fire City ahead before James McAtee – on his first Premier League start for City – extended the advantage via a stunning Ederson assist.

Nico O’Reilly then got in on the scoring, registering his first Premier League goal to set the seal on what was a result to remember.

The victory moved Pep Guardiola’s side back up into fourth place in the Premier League table with six games of the season remaining.

snippet.title: Jaat Movie REVIEW | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
Jaat Movie Review By Deeksha Sharma. Jaat Featuring Sunny Deol vs Randeep Hooda in a Mass Masala Action Thriller based on a Layered Storytelling inspired from Mythology History of Raavan & his end by a Single Warrior! 

Jaat Full Movie Story Outline & Positives Negatives would be shared in this Video. Can Sunny Deol repeat Gadar 2 Success or Bollywood Formula with South Director prove unlucky just like Sikandar? Find out now!

Jaat is a 2025 Indian Hindi-language action thriller film written and directed by Gopichand Malineni (in his Hindi debut), and produced by Mythri Movie Makers and People Media Factory.The film stars Sunny Deol in lead role alongside Randeep Hooda, Vineet Kumar Singh, Regina Cassandra, Saiyami Kher, Ramya Krishnan, Jagapathi Babu and others in supporting roles. The film score and soundtrack is composed by Thaman S.

Principal photography commenced in June 2024 and was extensively filmed across Hyderabad, Bapatla and Visakhapatnam.

Jaat was theatrically released on 10 April 2025.

snippet.title: Brides Ke Nakhre - Love vs Arrange Marriage | Indian Family Wedding | Anaysa
snippet.description:
In India, love marriage and arranged marriage are often seen through very different lenses by families. When it's an arranged marriage, parents feel proud and responsible — they happily spend lavishly on the bride's clothes, jewelry, and a grand venue, treating it as a moment of honor and joy. They do everything possible to make it perfect. But when it’s a love marriage, especially without their full approval, the bride often faces constant taunts and judgment. Even after marriage, her choices may be questioned, and moments that should be happy are overshadowed by subtle or open disapproval from relatives. The difference in treatment reflects deep-rooted cultural expectations and social pressures.

localized.title: Brides Ke Nakhre - Love vs Arrange Marriage | Indian Family Wedding | Anaysa
localized.description:
In India, love marriage and arranged marriage are often seen through very different lenses by families. When it's an arranged marriage, parents feel proud and responsible — they happily spend lavishly on the bride's clothes, jewelry, and a grand venue, treating it as a moment of honor and joy. They do everything possible to make it perfect. But when it’s a love marriage, especially without their full approval, the bride often faces constant taunts and judgment. Even after marriage, her choices may be questioned, and moments that should be happy are overshadowed by subtle or open disapproval from relatives. The difference in treatment reflects deep-rooted cultural expectations and social pressures.
